# ⚽ FIFA World Cup 2026 — Prediction Challenge

A **Shiny** web app for hosting a prediction challenge with friends across all 104 World Cup matches.  
Votes and results are stored in a **Google Sheet** — fully persistent, even on the free tier of shinyapps.io.

---

## Features

- All 104 matches across 12 groups + knockout rounds through to the Final
- Click-to-vote team buttons — one pick per player per match, changeable before kick-off
- Live leaderboard scored automatically when the admin enters results
- Password-protected Admin panel to enter winners + scores
- Google Sheets backend — votes never disappear when the app sleeps

