## Setup (do this once)

### 1. Install packages
```r
source("app/install_packages.R")
```

### 2. Create the Google Sheet
```r
source("setup/setup_sheets.R")
```
This opens a browser → sign in → a Sheet called **"WC2026 Challenge"** is created with all 104 matches pre-loaded.  
Copy the **Sheet ID** printed in the console.

### 3. Add the Sheet ID to your environment
```r
usethis::edit_r_environ()
```
Add this line, then **restart R**:
```
WC2026_SHEET_ID="your_sheet_id_here"
```

### 4. Run locally
```r
shiny::runApp("app/")
```

